Package: montyhall
Title: Simulate the Monty Hall Problem
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nirel", "Berz", , "nberz@asu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package creates a game to simulate the Monty Hall problem. Players will choose a door, the game will open a goat door, then players will either keep their original choice or change to the remaining door. The game will then produce a "WIN" or "LOSE" outcome.
Depends: 
	dplyr
License: `use_mit_license()`, `use_gpl3_license()` or friends to pick a
    license
Encoding: UTF-8
